to change his name and for setting such a

00:17:14.529 --> 00:17:18.299
wonderful example for others.

00:17:18.300 --> 00:17:23.000
Muhammad Ali was the greatest heavyweight
boxer of all time.

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:27.260
As a boxer, he was brilliant.

00:17:27.260 --> 00:17:30.880
As a historian, not so much.

